Titolo: The Path of Motus

Anno: 2018

Descrizione: The Path of Motus is an independent video game designed by Michael Hicks for PlayStation 4, Xbox One and PC. The game follows a goblin named Motus who is trapped inside a mysterious forest. He plans to escape by building bridges through the forest, but his determination is challenged by bullies that use their own words to destroy him. The game was made using the MonoGame framework.